{
  "info": {
    "name": "FoxGo API — Docker / Localhost only",
    "_postman_id": "9e2b1d40-8c3f-4a1e-9b7d-3f5a2c8e1d22",
    "description": "Chỉ **Docker / localhost**: biến **`docker_gateway_url`** mặc định `http://localhost:3000`. **Import:** file này là collection **riêng** — Import lần 1 (Deploy) + lần 2 (Docker) hoặc chọn cả hai JSON cùng lúc. Không dùng chung biến với `FoxGo-API-Deploy.postman_collection.json` (`foxgo_gateway_url`).\n\nKhông thêm `/api` vào gateway URL. **Lấy OTP mock:** gửi OTP trước (`POST .../register-phone/start`), rồi `GET .../api/auth/dev/otp?phone=...` — không Bearer. Cần `OTP_SMS_MODE=mock` + `OTP_ENABLE_DEV_ENDPOINT=true` trên auth + gateway khi test mock.\n\n**Flow đăng ký (cả Customer và Driver):** 1→ Gửi OTP | 2→ Lấy OTP (mock) | 3→ Xác nhận OTP | 4→ Hoàn tất đăng ký | 5→ Đăng nhập.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "docker_gateway_url", "value": "http://localhost:3000", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "customerPhone", "value": "0901234501", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "driverPhone", "value": "0901234502", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "otp", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "customerToken", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "driverToken", "value": "", "type": "string" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "⚙️ System",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Health (gateway)",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{docker_gateway_url}}/health", "host": ["{{docker_gateway_url}}"], "path": ["health"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Ready (gateway + deps)",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{docker_gateway_url}}/ready", "host": ["{{docker_gateway_url}}"], "path": ["ready"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "🔑 Auth — Customer (local)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "1. Gửi OTP đăng ký",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"phone\": \"{{customerPhone}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{docker_gateway_url}}/api/auth/register-phone/start",
              "host": ["{{docker_gateway_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "register-phone", "start"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "2. Lấy OTP (mock) — GET, không Bearer",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (res.otp) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('otp', res.otp);",
                  "  console.log('OTP saved:', res.otp);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{docker_gateway_url}}/api/auth/dev/otp?phone={{customerPhone}}&purpose=register",
              "host": ["{{docker_gateway_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "dev", "otp"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "phone", "value": "{{customerPhone}}", "description": "0xxxxxxxxx hoặc +84…" },
                { "key": "purpose", "value": "register" }
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "3. Xác nhận OTP",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"phone\": \"{{customerPhone}}\",\n  \"otp\": \"{{otp}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{docker_gateway_url}}/api/auth/register-phone/verify",
              "host": ["{{docker_gateway_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "register-phone", "verify"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "4. Hoàn tất đăng ký",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"phone\": \"{{customerPhone}}\",\n  \"password\": \"Test@123456\",\n  \"role\": \"CUSTOMER\",\n  \"firstName\": \"Khách\",\n  \"lastName\": \"Test\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{docker_gateway_url}}/api/auth/register-phone/complete",
              "host": ["{{docker_gateway_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "register-phone", "complete"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "5. Đăng nhập Customer",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "const token = res?.data?.tokens?.accessToken || res?.accessToken;",
                  "if (token) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('customerToken', token);",
                  "  console.log('customerToken saved');",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"phone\": \"{{customerPhone}}\",\n  \"password\": \"Test@123456\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{docker_gateway_url}}/api/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{docker_gateway_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "login"]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "🚗 Auth — Driver (local)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "1. Gửi OTP đăng ký driver",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"phone\": \"{{driverPhone}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{docker_gateway_url}}/api/auth/register-phone/start",
              "host": ["{{docker_gateway_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "register-phone", "start"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "2. Lấy OTP driver (mock) — GET, không Bearer",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (res.otp) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('otp', res.otp);",
                  "  console.log('OTP saved:', res.otp);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{docker_gateway_url}}/api/auth/dev/otp?phone={{driverPhone}}&purpose=register",
              "host": ["{{docker_gateway_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "dev", "otp"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "phone", "value": "{{driverPhone}}" },
                { "key": "purpose", "value": "register" }
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "3. Xác nhận OTP driver",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"phone\": \"{{driverPhone}}\",\n  \"otp\": \"{{otp}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{docker_gateway_url}}/api/auth/register-phone/verify",
              "host": ["{{docker_gateway_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "register-phone", "verify"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "4. Hoàn tất đăng ký driver",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"phone\": \"{{driverPhone}}\",\n  \"password\": \"Test@123456\",\n  \"role\": \"DRIVER\",\n  \"firstName\": \"Tài Xế\",\n  \"lastName\": \"Test\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{docker_gateway_url}}/api/auth/register-phone/complete",
              "host": ["{{docker_gateway_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "register-phone", "complete"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "5. Đăng nhập Driver",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "const token = res?.data?.tokens?.accessToken || res?.accessToken;",
                  "if (token) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('driverToken', token);",
                  "  console.log('driverToken saved');",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"phone\": \"{{driverPhone}}\",\n  \"password\": \"Test@123456\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{docker_gateway_url}}/api/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{docker_gateway_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "login"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "6. Đăng ký thông tin tài xế",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{driverToken}}" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"vehicle\": {\n    \"type\": \"MOTORBIKE\",\n    \"brand\": \"Honda\",\n    \"model\": \"Wave Alpha\",\n    \"plate\": \"59BA-000.01\",\n    \"color\": \"Black\",\n    \"year\": 2022\n  },\n  \"license\": {\n    \"class\": \"A1\",\n    \"number\": \"123456789012\",\n    \"expiryDate\": \"2027-12-31T00:00:00.000Z\"\n  }\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{docker_gateway_url}}/api/drivers/register",
              "host": ["{{docker_gateway_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "drivers", "register"]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
